weka.core.OptionHandler, java.io.Serializable
public class NominalToRandomEvenSplitOCFilter
extends AbstractNominalToRandomOCFilter

A nominal to output code filter; it splits the values of the attribute processed by generating a random partition in which at most 3/4 of the attribute values are in one set.

Version:
$Revision: 1.0 $
Author:
